# API Test Cases

## Scope
Covers functional, validation, security and response behavior.

---

## TC_API_001 – Valid Request Returns 200
Expected: Correct response body + schema

---

## TC_API_002 – Invalid Input Returns 400
Expected: Meaningful error message returned

---

## TC_API_003 – Unauthorized Request Returns 401
Expected: No sensitive data exposed

---

## TC_API_004 – Forbidden Access 403
Expected: Access blocked correctly

---

## TC_API_005 – Server Error Handling 500
Expected: No stack traces returned

---

## TC_API_006 – Response Time Performance
Expected: < 2 seconds average

---

## TC_API_007 – Data Integrity
Expected: No data loss or corruption
